  <span id="freeText16761495866662671992" style="display:none">I think I'd have enjoyed this more three years ago when we went to Gettysburg. The research is plentiful, the tone is objective and the material is concisely presented. I just couldn't find myself being swept away with reading a tome about the causes of the civil war.</span>
